      <div
        class="text-center text-[#020202] text-[40px] font-medium !font-playfair"
      >
        Grocery Go
      </div>
      <div class="self-stretch text-center">
        <span style="text-[#020202] text-base font-normal font-['Open Sans']"
          >Design an iOS shopping app that
        </span><span
          style="text-[#020202] text-base font-semibold font-['Open Sans']"
          >increased revenue by 25%</span
        ><span style="text-[#020202] text-base font-normal font-['Open Sans']"
          >. The app's concept is to assist shoppers in applying automatic
          discounts, saving money, and accelerating the checkout process.</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex relative">
      <Image src={phone1} alt="Phone1" class="w-1/3" />

      <Image src={phone2} alt="Phone2" class="w-1/3" />

      <Image src={phone3} alt="Phone3" class="w-1/3" />
